{"image_id": "ATO_2017_page_17", "image_size": [1257, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "(6) The performance-based rate program provides incentives to distribution companies to minimize purchased", "bbox": [161.6, 135.2, 1079.1, 161.2]}, {"text": "gas costs by allowing the companies and its customers to share the purchased gas costs savings.", "bbox": [188.7, 165.4, 987.8, 186.2]}, {"text": "Although substantial progress has been made in recent years by improving rate design and recovery of", "bbox": [194.9, 203.1, 1050.3, 224.0]}, {"text": "investment across Atmos Energy’s operating areas, we will continue to seek improvements in rate design to", "bbox": [153.2, 228.1, 1053.4, 249.0]}, {"text": "address cost variations and pursue tariffs that reduce regulatory lag associated with investments. Further, poten-", "bbox": [153.2, 253.1, 1087.2, 274.0]}, {"text": "tial changes in federal energy policy, federal safety regulations and adverse economic conditions will necessitate", "bbox": [153.2, 278.1, 1094.6, 299.0]}, {"text": "continued vigilance by the Company and our regulators in meeting the challenges presented by these external", "bbox": [153.2, 303.2, 1067.6, 324.0]}, {"text": "factors.", "bbox": [153.2, 328.2, 215.1, 349.0]}, {"text": "Recent Ratemaking Activity", "bbox": [174.1, 378.4, 412.8, 399.2]}, {"text": "Substantially all of our regulated revenues in the fiscal years ended September 30, 2017, 2016 and 2015", "bbox": [194.9, 416.3, 1062.4, 437.2]}, {"text": "were derived from sales at rates set by or subject to approval by local or state authorities. Net operating income", "bbox": [153.2, 441.3, 1082.5, 462.2]}, {"text": "increases resulting from ratemaking activity totaling $104.2 million, $122.5 million and $114.5 million, became", "bbox": [153.2, 466.3, 1089.6, 487.2]}, {"text": "effective in fiscal 2017, 2016 and 2015, as summarized below:", "bbox": [153.2, 491.3, 676.8, 512.2]}, {"text": "Annual Increase to Operating", "bbox": [774.5, 523.7, 987.1, 540.4]}, {"